storyInfo: Because of a simple misunderstanding, Jaye finds himself in the center of a Lungmen gang battle.

attributes.text: There is a legend in Lungmen.
The dark slums are a turbulent place where different factions cross paths. There, one must tread extremely carefully, lest one find oneself swept away by the roiling waves.
Yet there is one man who stands at the pinnacle, above all these different factions, and maintains order from the shadows. It could even be said that the entire slums move to his will alone.
There are many rumors about him, though few have actually seen him in person.
During his day-to-day life, he is no different from any other local. You could walk right past him without realizing his true identity.

You will never know if the random passerby you happen to lay eyes on is one of his informants. You will also never know if, in some dark corner, he is obliterating those foolish enough to stand up to him.
And there are many who believe that this is no mere legend...

attributes.content: That's him? You absolutely sure? You're pulling my leg.
I've been watching him for a while now. Fits the leaked description to a T. It's gotta be him.
Man... He doesn't look like no pushover...
What do we do? Are we really jumping him?
The goods we lost are too important. We don't have a choice... What was the password again?
I remember it. It's...
Well, look at you. Business is going well. Not taking any time off for New Year's?
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: There's a lot of foot traffic at night. Figured I'd make a bit of money.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Here you go, Miss. Your spicy finballs.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Whoa, that smells so great! Here's the cash.
attributes.name: Female Tourist

attributes.content: Mmm... Delish! Just what you'd expect from a finball stall that comes highly recommended in the Great Foodie Guide!
attributes.name: Female Tourist

attributes.content: Hold on!
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Huh?!
attributes.name: Female Tourist

attributes.content: W-What's the matter?
attributes.name: Female Tourist

attributes.content: You paid too much. Here's your change.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: T-Thank you...
attributes.name: Female Tourist

attributes.content: Um... May I go now?
attributes.name: Female Tourist

attributes.content: What, you need something else?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: N-Not at all! See you!
attributes.name: Female Tourist

attributes.content: Looks like I scared off another customer...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Did I say something wrong?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Hohoh... You've been tending to the stall for a couple of days now. What's going on with Old Tung?
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: The weather's been cold, and he says that hurts his legs, so I'm helping him out more often.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Do you know Uncle Tung, Master Lin?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: He's the finest finball chef in town. Of course I know him.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: Since I'm here, I might as well give him a bit of business too. I'll have an order of finballs. Let's see how much you've learned from him.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: Got it. One sec.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Four orders of finballs. Three curries and one mushroom soup.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Yeah, got it. I'll start yours after I finish the last guy's order.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Ahem. I said. Four orders of finballs. Three curries and one mushroom soup.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Yeah, got it. Three curries, one mushroom soup.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: (What's going on?! Didn't you say that was the password?)
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: (It's gotta be! You know that Feline assassin? That's what she tells him every time!)
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Master, your finballs.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Very good. Here's the money.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: No need. You're Uncle Tung's friend, I can't take your money.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: That won't do. Debts must be paid, and what must be done, must be done.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: Isn't that right?
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: (What's going on? Did that old fart just glance at us?)
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: (Tsk... What a pain.)
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Sir...?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: You still want your finballs?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: If you don't know which flavor you want, I can give you two to try out—
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: What're you getting all feisty for?!
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: If we don't get the drop on him now, then when? After he wastes us?!
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Now cut the crap! Let's drag him off!
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Leave a message for the Lou Seois. We have their boss, and they gotta bring the goods tonight if they want him alive!
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Now, now, young men. Don't overdo it. There are certain rules here in Lungmen that you don't break.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: Shut up, Grandpa! This is business! Sit down and eat your finballs!
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Interesting.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: Ugh...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: My head hurts...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: What's this...? Where am I?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Yo, you're finally awake. Here, have some water.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Thanks—What's going on? Who are you people... and why am I tied up...?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Sorry, but we had no choice but to go to these lengths for someone of your stature. We didn't know the Lou Seois were working for you. Please forgive us.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: That said, the Lou Seois started this. They're the ones who took our goods first. Not very reasonable, don't you think?
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: What goods? Fins? The boat was there at the docks, and I got there first. Of course I got all the freshest fins. What makes them yours?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: (Did he just say, 'the docks'? Didn't our goods get lifted at the docks?)
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: (Right, I get it. 'Fins' is an euphemism. What he's saying is finders keepers. The goods belong to whoever gets their hands on them first.)
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: *Cough*... Alright, you have a point.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: But there are rules in this business. We Char Sius have been dealing in this stuff the whole time. Don't you think you should at least give us a heads-up if you were going to edge into our business?
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: I've been running my seafood stall for years now. How come I've never seen you people around then?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: (Is 'seafood stall' an euphemism too?)
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: (What he's saying is he's been in this business longer than us. We got here after him.)
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Right... We know that. You're known far and wide all across Lungmen. We respect someone of your stature. That's why we're taking the time to discuss this all friendly-like.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: If you want to get in on this business, we can talk, but the goods you stole are very important to us Char Sius. Please give them back, and this'll be easier on the both of us.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Known... all across Lungmen?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Um... I think you got the wrong person. Can I go now...?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Don't push it! That how you wanna play this?!
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: If it weren't for the respect we have for you, we wouldn't be here talking. We Char Sius ain't just gonna let you push us around!
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: I really don't know what you're talking about...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Still playing dumb, huh? Bring me the thing.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Take a look at this picture. Ring a bell?
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Is this... Waai Fu?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Don't think we don't know. She's a hitman who works for you Lou Seois, and your bodyguard.
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: What...?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Late last month, she stopped by your stall for finballs. The very next day, the Lou Seois' biggest rivals got their crib trashed. They say it was a Feline with some weird kung fu skills.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: And you're saying you didn't order it?
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Why did she have to pick that time of all times to play hero...?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: And what about this one?
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Madame Oni from the L.G.D.?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Looks like it's not just us. The L.G.D. has had eyes on you for a long time.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Our guys have seen that Madame Oni hanging out next to your finball shack more than once.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Now why don't you tell me why an Inspector from the L.G.D.'s Special Ops Team be interested in some finball hawker?
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: This is all just a misunderstanding...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Hmph, don't you think you can fool us with your little switcheroo.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Admit it. That dude you guys call the boss is just a decoy, and you're the real boss of the Lou Seois!
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: (I should probably just shut up for now.)
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Nothing more to say, huh?
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Alright, no more talking. Let's see how much your goons care about their boss.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Meanwhile...
Yo, Second Bro, we finally have news about the boss!
Where is he?!
The Char Sius just sent us a message. Apparently they took him hostage.
They sent us an address, and told us to bring the goods if we want the boss alive.
Dammit, I knew it was them! Get the whole gang! We're settling the score with the Char Sius tonight!
So are we bringing the goods or...?
'Course not! They think we're pushovers, huh? Get your weapons! Those punks are going down!
Thought it through yet, 'Boss'?
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Your lackeys got the message already. Hand over the goods, and no one has to get hurt. Wouldn't want your pretty face getting messed up in a struggle, would you?
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Why'd you send them a message? What if they actually send people here to fight you guys?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: You got balls, punk, still trying to threaten us!
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: That's not what I was—*Sigh*... never mind.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: (What do we do? He's got a point. If it comes to a fight, we're way outnumbered here.)
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: (Well, why didn't you bring more guys then?!)
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: (You're the one who wanted to keep this on the down low!)
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: (Well, I didn't expect him to not talk!)
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: (Whatever, just keep an eye on him... If you can convince him to cough up the goods, all the better. I'll go get the others.)
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: *Cough*...
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Thought it through yet, 'Boss'?
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: If you know what's good for you, you'll hand over the goods now, and we can still do this peacefully.
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Mind if I ask what 'goods' we're talking about here?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Cut the crap! Your gang beat up our guys at the port just to get your hands on them! You know what they are!
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Heh, only you freaks would try to take a dangerous job like this from us.
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Did you just say 'dangerous'?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Stop playing dumb! If you guys had the balls to snatch this job from right under the L.G.D.'s nose, you knew what you were getting into! You knew it was gonna be a big payday!
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Um... It's just you and me here right now, right?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Fine, I'll tell you where they are.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Oh? Now that's more like it. Talk.
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Come closer, you never know who's listening.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Alright, now spit it out.
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Closer.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Enough chit-chat. Just—
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Uncle Tung was right. Better to use your head than your fists.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: You guys really tied me up good, huh... Sorry, I'm borrowing this knife. I'll give it back if we ever see each other again.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I don't know who you're looking for or what you want, but you've got the wrong guy. I ain't anybody's boss.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: *Sigh*... But listening's not your strong point, is it? Anyway, I'mma split here.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Ugh, my head hurts...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: This is the place. Now where are the Char Sius?
Look over there. Some guy just came out of that building with a knife. I bet that's our contact with them.
Hold up, doesn't that guy look kind of familiar?
Now I remember! He's that top assassin who's always disguised as a seafood hawker! Last time he skinned twenty people alive with a scaling knife! I saw it with my own eyes!
I didn't know he was with the Char Sius! What do we do now...?
Calm down. Let's try talking to him first.
No one came after me. Guess I lost them...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: *Sigh*... It's New Year's. I haven't even closed the stall yet. What is going on...?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Hey, you.
Huh? Me?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: This the Char Sius' hideout?
(The guys from before said they're from the Char Sius, didn't they?)
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Yeah, that's right.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Get him!
attributes.name: Vicious-Looking Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Where's our boss?!
attributes.name: Vicious-Looking Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: How would I know?!
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Heh, I know you Char Sius got numbers, but that doesn't mean jack against us!
attributes.name: Vicious-Looking Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: You got the wrong guy—
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: He took down Second Bro in just one hit! I knew it! That's their top assassin!
attributes.name: Angry Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Not another version of this...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Don't worry! We got the numbers! Even he can't take on all of us at once!
attributes.name: Angry Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: With me, guys! We're saving the boss!
attributes.name: Angry Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Well... Guess I better make a run for it first...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Don't let him get away! After him!
attributes.name: Angry Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Alright, they brought their people with them.
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Let's go, boys! Get 'em!
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Heh, an ambush, huh?
attributes.name: Angry Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Don't be afraid, boys! Let's show 'em who's boss!
attributes.name: Angry Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Hand over the goods!
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Hand over the boss!
attributes.name: Angry Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Uh, how come you guys are fighting? Take it easy. There's no need for violence.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Uh... *Sigh*... I guess I'll go back and close the stall.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: What're these 'goods' I keep hearing about, anyway...?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Good evening, Uncle Wong.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Well, hello there, Jaye. What's up? I don't have any fresh fins for you at this hour.
attributes.name: Uncle Wong

attributes.content: No, I just have a question.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Have you seen any big fights here lately?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Oh, don't make me laugh. There are more fights here on the docks than we have fins for sale. What kinda fight are we talking about here?
attributes.name: Uncle Wong

attributes.content: I don't mean a normal street fight. I mean like two gangs of mean-looking people fighting each other.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Eh, that's probably not the best way to describe it... Uncle, have you seen any new faces at the docks lately?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: The docks are huge. How am I supposed to remember every single person I see?
attributes.name: Uncle Wong

attributes.content: *Sigh*... Now that you mention it, though, this is starting to ring a bell.
attributes.name: Uncle Wong

attributes.content: For a while last month, there was a group of people hauling crates here every night.
attributes.name: Uncle Wong

attributes.content: Normally I wouldn't give it a second thought, but all their crates were wrapped up in black. It all looked very shady.
attributes.name: Uncle Wong

attributes.content: Do you remember what those people looked like? Where did they take the crates?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I was busy closing up. You think I'd remember something like that? Not everyone's got a good memory like you.
attributes.name: Uncle Wong

attributes.content: (So those must be the goods the Char Sius kept talking about.)
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: (What are they planning...?)
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Ai-yah, I didn't even notice, but look at those bruises. You were fighting again, weren't you?
attributes.name: Uncle Wong

attributes.content: Here, put some ice on it.
attributes.name: Uncle Wong

attributes.content: Thanks...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: You know, you seem like the honest sort, but how come you always have all these scrapes and bruises?
attributes.name: Uncle Wong

attributes.content: Uh... I didn't really mean to—
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I've known you for a long time now. You're a good kid. You're patient, and you can't stand injustice. That's why you always end up fighting those punks.
attributes.name: Uncle Wong

attributes.content: No, it's actually all just a mis—
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I know your heart's in the right place, but you need to protect yourself too. If something happens, let somebody else take care of it. Don't go looking for trouble with people you shouldn't mess with. Got it?
attributes.name: Uncle Wong

attributes.content: Yeah, I got it. Thanks. I have something to take care of tonight though, and I know how to handle it.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Oh, right, is it okay if I borrow your phone?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Goddamned Char Sius. They sure put up a good fight...
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Now where is everyone...? So quick to run. Where'd they go...?
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Oh, good. There's still one of you left.
I-It's you!
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Right, it's me.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: The Char Sius' top assassin.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Yeek!
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Please... Please don't hurt me!
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: I can overlook everything you just did, for now.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: But listen up. I'll only ask this once. And if I don't like your answer...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Well, you'll see.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I'll talk! I'll talk! I'll tell you everything that I know!
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Where are the goods the Lou Seois stole from us last week?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I don't know!
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Why did you steal them? Who's the buyer?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I don't know...
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Again you don't know?!
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I really don't know!
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: I-I've only been with the gang for two months... I really don't know any of our big secrets!
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Then what DO you know?!
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: It was last week! Our members stole something from the Char Sius at the port. The boss was real happy, but he went missing just a few days later.
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: We looked everywhere, but couldn't find a thing.
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: (So their boss really is missing.)
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: And then?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Then, we got your guys' message today. I figured there was going to be a fight, so I tagged along. Seriously, that's all I know!
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: (Hm... Looks like that's all I'm getting from this guy.)
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: *Cough*. I'll tell you this much. Your boss? We Char Sius kidnapped him.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Go home and tell your boss. Uh... tell whoever's calling the shots without him.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I'll give you one last chance to settle this peacefully. Meet us at the docks with what you stole. Midnight.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: And I'd better see some sincerity, or your boss is dead meat.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Now scram.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Okay!
attributes.name: Injured Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Phew...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Looks like he bought it.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: It's not easy playing the villain.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Calm down. Calm down... Next up...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: You idiot! Imbecile!
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: We had the guy tied up. How'd you let him get away? Now how are we supposed to negotiate with the Lou Seois?
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: What're you yelling at me for? You brought all those guys and still couldn't catch him!
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Why you—
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: I heard somebody's looking for me.
It's you!
attributes.name: Char Siu Members

attributes.content: Yep, it's me.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Heh, I gotta hand it to you two. You've got keen eyes, being able to see through my act.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: That's right. I'm the boss of the Lou Seois.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I knew it... W-What do you want?
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: It's very simple. The things we took from you? You can have them back. But we'll need an explanation for why you kidnapped me.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: We'll be waiting for you at the docks with the goods, tonight at midnight. I want all of the Char Sius there.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I'll let you have what's yours, but I won't tolerate this disrespect.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: (What should we do? Do we still want it...?)
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: (W-Wait... He's all by himself. We managed to knock him out earlier, maybe we can...)
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Hold it right there!
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: T-That's the Feline hitman! It's her!
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Heh, I let my guard down and got ambushed once, but did you really think I'd let it happen again?!
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Sounds to me you don't know who you're dealing with.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: *Cough*...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: (What do I do now?)
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: (The wall. The wall!)
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: (Oh, right.)
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: Hah!
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: She knocked the wall down... in one strike!
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: I'll be waiting at the docks in two hours. You better show up if you know what's good for you!
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: What do we do now...?
attributes.name: Shrewd-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: What do you mean, what do we do? There's no running from it. We just have to go!
attributes.name: Fierce-looking Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Wait, wait! Hold on! Why are we running so fast?
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: You still haven't told me what this charade's all about.
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: Phew... This should be far enough.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: *Sigh* To tell you the truth, I don't really know what's going on myself.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Anyway, thanks for the help. I'll treat you to some finballs next time.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: No worries. It's no big deal.
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: You really looked like some mafia boss just now, though. I nearly fell for it myself.
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: Do I really look like such a bad guy?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: You're not hiding any secret identities from me, are you?
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: Come on, stop teasing me.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Eh, I'll head to the docks first. All of this should start to make sense come midnight.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Good. Right on time.
attributes.name: Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Heh, I could say the same to you.
attributes.name: Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Where're the goods?
attributes.name: Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Slow down. Where's our boss?
attributes.name: Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Don't make me laugh. You think you can just keep screwing with us like this?
attributes.name: Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Now cut the crap and give us what's ours!
attributes.name: Char Siu Member

attributes.content: In your dreams! Let us see the boss first!
attributes.name: Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Taking us for a ride, are you? You want to go again?
attributes.name: Char Siu Member

attributes.content: Let's do it! I ain't afraid of you!
attributes.name: Lou Seoi Member

attributes.content: Okay, let's drop the weapons. If you got anything to say, say it at the station.
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: Shit! It's a set-up!
attributes.name: Char Sius & Lou Seois

attributes.content: All of you, come with me.
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: You're the one who called this in, right?
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: Yeah, that's me...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Mind telling me how you found out a deal was going down between these two gangs?
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: Uh... It's a long story...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I'm still wrapping my head around it, but that's about the size of it... Do you believe me?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Hahaha, don't be so nervous. The L.G.D.'s actually been following this case for a while now.
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: Guess there's no harm in telling you. Most of their weapon cache actually got strewn all over the streets after their last rumble. The L.G.D. tried to retrieve as much as we could, but the Char Sius still managed to get their hands on a decent chunk of what's left.
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: I-Isn't that dangerous?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Yeah, though they didn't have the guts to smuggle the weapons themselves.
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: They were thinking of taking out the brand new Originium Devices on the weapons, and selling those instead. Of course, that's illegal too.
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: The L.G.D. apprehended the Lou Seois' boss the other day. He was looking for a buyer for the stolen goods, you see.
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: He's pretty tight-lipped. Couldn't get much out of him. We owe you a great deal tonight. It's all thanks to your plan that we managed to apprehend all these people.
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: Though come to think of it, you really shouldn't do anything so dangerous again.
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: I see, so that's how it is...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Um, ma'am? If there's nothing else, is it okay if I go now?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Hold on.
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: Truth be told, I've actually been keeping an eye on you too. With your skills, I think you're a bit overqualified to be a mere street hawker.
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: I know a much better gig for you. How about it?
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: Well... I appreciate the offer, ma'am.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Though just as Lungmen needs police officers like you, it needs seafood hawkers like me too. It's not about qualifications.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Anyway, I don't think what I'm doing right now is so bad...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Haha, I get you. Of course, I'll respect your decision. If you ever have a change of heart, though, you know where to find me.
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: Thanks for your work. I'm gonna head back now.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Oh, and be sure to pay the L.G.D. a visit after the holidays for your certificate!
attributes.name: Hoshiguma

attributes.content: Oh, sure, when I have time.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Good kid. As expected from one of Tung's students. I knew I was right about him.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: Several months later...
Hey, you see that finball stall there?
They're getting quite a lot of customers. Why don't we give it a try?
Hah, that's no normal finball stall. The stall's owner is actually the patriarch of the Lungmen Docks triads!
On New Year's Eve, he took on both the Char Sius and the Lou Seois all by himself, and you know what happened? He took down every last one! Also—
Shh! Quiet down. I think he heard that!
Yo, boss, how about some finballs?
attributes.name: Jaye
